<sect1 id="dir_a5b4e9d915dcb347a77aabec50326e84_1autotoc_md276">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::requests</title><para>Data structures for spawn and despawn requests.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_a5b4e9d915dcb347a77aabec50326e84_1autotoc_md277">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module contains lightweight data transfer objects used to communicate spawn and despawn parameters between dispatchers and managers.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_a5b4e9d915dcb347a77aabec50326e84_1autotoc_md278">
<title>Key Classes</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Structure  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>SpawnRequest</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Contains spawn profile ID and spawn context  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>DespawnRequest</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Contains entity GUID and optional spawn profile ID  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ScheduledSpawnPlanRequest</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Contains scheduled spawn plan and spawn context  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
